    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Hyouton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You send your Chakra through the ground, forcing ground water upward and freezing it, making a large spike of ice erupt from the ground to deal 2d8 damage (half cold, half piercing) to creatures in the area.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to target another square, causing an ice spike to erupt there as well (maximum 1 target square per 2 levels).</p>\n\n",
